query_sample: SELECT weight_gap(weight_kg, height_m) AS gap FROM bmi ORDER BY gap DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT normalize_name(name) AS nome_normalizzato, BMI FROM bmi ORDER BY nome_normalizzato ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT carbon_footprint(kwh_used) AS co2_kg FROM energy_consumption ORDER BY co2_kg DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT pass_flag(pass_status) AS pass_num FROM student_performance ORDER BY pass_num DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT extract_numeric_suffix(student_name) AS idx, average_score FROM student_performance ORDER BY idx ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT revenue_per_unit(total_revenue, units_sold) AS rev_per_unit FROM products ORDER BY rev_per_unit DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT demand_elasticity(units_sold, price) AS elasticity FROM products ORDER BY elasticity ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT normalize_text(name) AS name_norm FROM products ORDER BY name_norm ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT parse_percent(savings_rate) AS savings_rate_num FROM financial ORDER BY savings_rate_num DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT burn_rate(expenses, income) AS burn FROM financial ORDER BY burn DESC LIMIT 5;
